Package com.peaslimited.shoppeas.repository

Interface WholesalerAddressRepository

All Known Implementing Classes:
WholesalerAddressRepositoryImpl
public interface WholesalerAddressRepository
WholesalerAddressRepository is an interface for managing wholesaler address data, including retrieving, adding, and updating address information.
